title: Grateful Dead Live at Memorial Stadium on 1994-06-14
description:
Set 1

Shakedown Street, Little Red Rooster, Loose Lucy, When I Paint My Masterpiece*, Althea, Eternity

Set 2

Victim Or The Crime-> Lazy River Road, Samba In The Rain, Truckin'-> That Would Be Something-> Drums-> Space-> Way to Go Home, Standing On the Moon -> Sugar Magnolia, E: Liberty

*Weir on acoustic guitar
